## Commandes de déploiement

```bash
# Build PWA (toujours --no-cache + les 2 compose files)
docker compose -f compose.yaml -f compose.prod.yaml build --no-cache pwa
docker compose -f compose.yaml -f compose.prod.yaml up -d pwa

# Copier fichier PHP + refresh
docker cp <fichier> creazot-ulm-php-1:/app/<path>
docker exec creazot-ulm-php-1 rm -rf /app/var/cache/prod
docker exec creazot-ulm-php-1 bin/console cache:clear
docker restart creazot-ulm-php-1

# Schema Doctrine
docker exec creazot-ulm-php-1 bin/console doctrine:schema:update --force
```

