## Providers frontend (arbre)

```
SessionProvider → ClientProvider → SiteSettingsProvider → SessionContextProvider → UserGuard → AdminAdapter
```

- `ClientProvider` : charge clients du user, expose `{ client, clients, switchClient }`
- `SiteSettingsProvider` : fetch `/site-settings`, expose `{ siteSettings }`

